text: Kubatbek Ayilchiyevich Boronov (, Kubatbek Ayılçiyeviç Boronov; born 15 December 1964) is a Kyrgyz politician. In June 2020, he became the Prime Minister of Kyrgyzstan. He resigned on 6 October 2020. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Prime Ministers of Kyrgyzstan
